name: InhaledCorticosteroidsICSAllergyIntolerance
title: Inhaled Corticosteroids(ICS) Allergy Intolerance
purpose: (Clinical Focus: SNOMED CT codes and RxNORM codes that could be returned by the FHIR Allergy Intolerance resource, and would indicate allergy or intolerance to Inhaled Corticosteroids(ICS)  medications),(Data Element Scope: ALLERGY_INTOLERANCE:ICS),(Inclusion Criteria: RxNORM codes for individual medications that are Inhaled Corticosteroids medications, and various SNOMED CT codes that would indicate allergy or intolerance to Inhaled Corticosteroids medications as a class, or individual Inhaled Corticosteroids medications),(Exclusion Criteria: None)
